ent-CMUWYGuardequipmentvendor = We-Yu Guard equipment vendor
    .desc = An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Weyland-Yutani Security Guard apparel and equipment. Stocked with field gear for rapid deployment following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization. The interface is intentionally simple, even someone with tunnel-vision and frostbite can operate it.
